  <section class="season-themes">
    <h2>Themes Across the Season</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Reciprocity:</strong> Inner and outer. Self and other. Harmony and dissonance. The constant dance between polarities.</li>
      <li><strong>Discovery vs. Instruction:</strong> Framing learning, healing, growth as discovery-centered rather than instruction-centered.</li>
      <li><strong>Observation as Love:</strong> The quality of attention you bring to yourself and others is how you love.</li>
      <li><strong>Flexibility in Foundations:</strong> The more fundamental something is, the more relativity it needs.</li>
      <li><strong>Both/And:</strong> You can dance AND harmonize. Hold dissonance AND find beauty. The false binary is the problem.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

